overview: The first HydraLock Challenge starts things off! Worker Ant makes his official in-ring debut. Incoherence takes on The Order of the Neo Solar Temple! The Kings of Wrestling collide when Chris Hero & Claudio Castagnoli defend los Campeonatos de Parejas against tournament winners, Gran Akuma and Icarus of F.I.S.T.!
title: Chikara: Brick
